foundation.solution_text:
$-4$ is $1$ interval left of $-3$, on the left of zero.
[tikz]
\begin{tikzpicture}
\draw[{Stealth}-{Stealth}] (-3.1,0)--(3.1,0);
\foreach \v in {-5,...,5} {\draw (0.5*\v,0.12)--(0.5*\v,-0.12); \node[below] at (0.5*\v,-0.16) {$\v$};}
\fill (-2.0,0) circle (2.2pt);
\node[above] at (-2.0,0.2) {$-4$};
\end{tikzpicture}
[/tikz]

